#: input:6 standard
msgid ""
"The British imperium transported huge amounts of criminals to a new "
"continent soon after it was found at 17th. century. The imperial ships "
"abandoned you and all the other criminals it has to this barren, strange new "
"world. Your heroic decision is to bring order to the rows of the criminals "
"and to create your own prosperous country full of life. <br> "
"<br>------------- <br>seaport update"
msgstr ""

#: input:7 input:14 standard
msgid ""
"This is an improved version of the original map I created at around 2013. "
"Lots of changes and balancing have been done to make this map work properly "
"with build 20. I also added landmarks to the map. Enjoy."
msgstr ""
"Esta é uma versão melhorada do mapa original que criei por volta de 2013. "
"Muitas mudanças e balanceamentos foram feitos para fazer este mapa funcionar "
"corretamente com a build 20. Eu também adicionei pontos de referência ao "
"mapa.  Aproveite."
